        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>A one-day training program on "Disaster response, rescue operations, and vulnerability analysis" was organized by Mountain Forum Himalayas at Gupt Kashi in Rudra Prayag District, Uttarakhand. The program aimed to empower communities with knowledge and skills to handle disasters effectively. Thirty-four members (25 women, 9 men) from 10 villages participated in this training.</p>
